     Ok to begin you start out getting Knights of Truth Faction by killing at orc 1 and orc 2 or just plainly kill any guard in East or West Commons.  Watch out for Sgt Slate when you do this he will KILL you easy.  I can solo him at 45 pretty easily but he cons dark blue. To check and see if you have enough faction to start the Steel Warrior faction you head to West Commons and hail the guy sitting down by the inn near the water you can't miss him.  If your faction with him is warmly or amiable you are on the start of something good.<br>
     To max your faction with Steel warriors you can give milk which can be bought in PoK or just abut anywhere for like 5 copper. Bring the milk to Hojax which is that guy sitting down near that lake in WC. Give him 1 milk per slot. Repeat that over and over till you get warmly.  I brought about 10 stacks and I was good to go.<br>
     Now the fun part if you have PoK this quest takes 5 min per turn in.  At lvl 22 which my friend assist me he gets 1 gold of xp per turn in and at 42 I was getting over 2 and a half blues per turn in and still at 50 I get about 1 and a half blue per turn in.<br>
     Anyways head to Ak'Anon go to the Mino Caves and Kill Mino Slavers till the mino Hero Pops, he spawns outside the cave over by the big wheel that has the hole in the middle and he will run around in a circle till get gets to the cave entrance.  Kill him and take the mino shackle. Gate out and head to Qeynos.  Go to the Warrior guild which is under the arena and give him shackle he will give you the hero bracer about 4pp also. Repeat the quest.  <br>
      If you are an enchanter your pet will not work well the Hero hits for 90 to 100 and he is fast.<br>
     Best thing to get 1st is KEI 2nd best thing to get is SoW potions also set your bind point right in the middle of the path in PoK so you can travel faster.  Also one last point to mention DO NOT GO FAR INTO THE BACK OF THE CAVE THERE IS A NECRO NAMED MELGRATH AND HE IS NASTY. stay close when in the cave the farthest I have ever had to go to spawn the Hero is to the 2nd path to the right.  Also there is a Mino Lord that spawns in the 2nd path to the righ he is FASTER than SoW.<br>
